00:42:33.530 --> 00:42:36.010
and then this thing moves on--

00:42:36.010 --> 00:42:38.700
and I'm purposely making this
vector shorter than the

00:42:38.700 --> 00:42:39.800
incident vector--

00:42:39.800 --> 00:42:41.510
with that amount
